==Korean==

===Etymology===

From [[긴]] (''gin'', adjective form of [[길다]], "to be long") + [[꼬리]] (''kko.ri'', "tail") + [[꼬마]] (''kko.ma'', "midget") + [[쥐]] (''jwi'', "mouse" or "rat")

===Noun===

'''긴꼬리꼬마쥐''' (gin.kko.ri.kko.ma.jwi)

# a [[long-tailed birch mouse]], ''[[Sicista caudata]]''.

